    <text>
        <front>
            <div type="summary">
                <p>
                    Aline Burch apologises for the delay in replying to Mrs. Lucas's letter of 21 January and explains that Mr. Woolf has recently had an operation and is still in recovery. She will show him the letter as soon as he is able to handle correspondence again.
                </p>
            </div>
        </front>
